  <summary>Used with the <command tag="disable menu">disable menu</command>, <command tag="doMenu">doMenu</command>, <command tag="enable menu">enable menu</command>, and <command tag="select">select</command> <glossary tag="command">commands</glossary>, to designate a <glossary tag="menu item">menu item</glossary> in a <keyword tag="menu">menu</keyword>.</summary>
