  </examples>
  <description>
    <p>Use the <b>menuItem</b> <glossary tag="keyword">keyword</glossary> to enable or disable a <glossary tag="menu item">menu item</glossary>, or to perform a menu action.</p><p/><p><b>Comments:</b></p><p>Unlike menus, menu items must be specified by number. The topmost item in a menu is numbered 1.</p>
